<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num2.png" "align:left" />
Invite Fans to Join
</h2>
<p>
Share your fan club page on Facebook, Twitter, your website and other online outlets. Your passionate fans will join and share with their friends. 
</p>
</div>


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num3.png"/>
Empower Fans to Promote</h2>
<p>
Your goal is to get fans to spread your message. You can easily do this on Snowball by publishing updates to fans. Actions can include tweeting about an upcoming event, sharing a new song on Facebook, publishing a blog post, among others.  
</p>
</div>


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num4.png"/>
Track the Results
</h2>
<p>
Every action your fans take is tracked. You can see who your most active and influential fans are at any time. 
</p>
</div>


<div class="wcydtext">
<h2>
<img src="../images/num5.png"/>
Rewards Your Fans
</h2>
<p>
Show your most passionate and influential fans that you appreciate their support by giving them cool stuff like access to special events and exclusive offers. 
</p>
